{"tid":1958432,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有餵開流浪貓嘅請入","createTime":"2020-04-04T15:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T20:53:25.000Z","uid":275208,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9344566deda3c7bf35307eb90831bfe8dd7582","tid":1958432,"uid":275208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"最近屋企樓下發現浪貓，佢有個固定位匿埋，每次行近到大約1m距離佢就走開<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />目前餵咗個零星期，每晚俾個罐頭佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驟眼睇又唔似有人養，但有每朝個罐頭都有人清理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問應該搵義工帶走定係餵多排睇緣份收養好？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S97mhfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS97mhfq.png&h=85e79c57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09d835e28ed40d53b9fa7a8ffb679b9ff230f37f","tid":1958432,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:48:36.000Z","msg":"邊區？ 你想唔想養佢"},{"pid":"17efab5b22c6f3cb5923eca8fceec6cb1399d595","tid":1958432,"uid":205339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"義工帶唔到幾多<br />\n最後人道毁滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ea8d58915705a4e6fc44a63b0b29ec5e73198b","tid":1958432,"uid":238920,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"奉勸一句,千萬唔好講個位置出去俾任何人聽<br />\n同埋盡量令街貓唔好對人太過親近<br />\nD所謂貓義工過半都係心理變態"},{"pid":"09b594044b7f1df747b631427324595752bf339b","tid":1958432,"uid":256296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48ea8d58915705a4e6fc44a63b0b29ec5e73198b","tid":1958432,"uid":238920,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"奉勸一句,千萬唔好講個位置出去俾任何人聽<br />\n同埋盡量令街貓唔好對人太過親近<br />\nD所謂貓義工過半都係心理變態"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"冇撚有錯<br />\n見到靚貓就死攬唔放手唔畀人養"},{"pid":"f2e84529a9aeaed68145d7