3b1c935","tid":1958432,"uid":76382,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"連罐餵大忌嚟喎 ...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T18:38:44.000Z","msg":"用咩兜好？試過用陶瓷碗俾佢食，第日唔見咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T01:17:45.000Z","msg":"紙碟？<br />\n我都試過唔見喂食碗"},{"pid":"2920db68c2b844de8b43fb09b92ea91d32821758","tid":1958432,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T01:23:36.000Z","msg":"用紙碟啦，同埋最好隔返一頭半個鐘等佢食完掉左佢，唔係d曱甴會走黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe2fe61af208c176041a6136ba7ac85e6b23e3d","tid":1958432,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T01:40:05.000Z","msg":"用膠兜紙兜都得。唔好俾成個罐。<br />\n另外就係餵佢開罐前發出下聲音等佢知道你係到。<br />\n例如，輕敲罐身，你扮下貓叫<br />\n佢會慢慢認得你把聲。<br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪想自己養返？<br />\n係嘅可以搵我傾傾。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fkyouhk_gov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffkyouhk_gov&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=cf088dfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fkyouhk_gov</a>"},{"pid":"442ecb1b6f85b63a613d41f8b9e75d75de13cf4b","tid":1958432,"uid":67272,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"自己收編啦<br />\n隻貓你餵開既話﹐唔洗聽貓義工撚<br />\n你俾隻貓俾佢地<br />\n十隻有九隻唔會出到領養<br />\n之後又會話無人要要放返街"},{"pid":"78cc40e51f221577c0f9b76508df02f2c155ee32","tid":1958432,"uid":125665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"成貓比較小人會領養，如果你有能力養到而佢又親你既話不如考慮自己養喇"},{"pid":"aecde72c1bbf7836f55d7aad27060f246bbdf4b7","tid":1958432,"uid":138541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:56:30.000Z","msg":"喂左一排但唔識執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢見到我拎袋 毛巾都會好驚 但平時又會嗲"},{"pid":"8d6461ff809103ca458b7ceae0f1f984268d3626","tid":1958432,"uid":20908,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:35:59.000Z","msg":"樓豬可不借post問小小野<